[[uid=830lwg9y]] he succeeded in the course of the
[[uid=830lwg9z]] afternoon in alienating the affections
[[uid=830lwgb0]] of my only ward. He subsequently stayed
[[uid=830lwgb1]] to tea, and devoured every single
[[uid=830lwgb2]] muffin. And what makes his conduct all
[[uid=830lwgb3]] the more heartless is, that he was
[[uid=830lwgb4]] perfectly well aware from the first
[[uid=830lwgb5]] that I have no brother, that I never
[[uid=830lwgb6]] had a brother, and that I don’t intend
[[uid=830lwgb7]] to have a brother, not even of any
[[uid=830lwgb8]] kind. I distinctly told him so myself
