[[uid=830lwgbn]] consent.
[[uid=830lwgbp]] 
[[uid=830lwgbq]] LADY BRACKNELL. [[attitudeInstr]]
[[uid=830lwgbr]] [To Cecily.] Come here, sweet child.
[[uid=830lwgbs]] [Cecily goes over.] How old are you,
